Key Technical Developments (close of 05/31)
-------------------------------------------------------

The June British Pound is at a key junture! Hourly stochastics
are overbought again and the recent recovery appears corrective.
A drop below the recent lows opens the door to big downside potential.

Gold dropped $9 oz and is testing key support at 265! If prices can
stabilize near current levels, then we could see a resumption of
the uptrend. The market phsychology at a wave 2 low is often more
bearish than the ultimate low.

December Eurodollars are trading at a 40 point discount to September.
I like the long side of Dec heading into Friday's number!

